snippet.title: Remove AMBER HEARD From Aquaman 2 Petition Could Hits 500K Signatures
snippet.description:
Remove AMBER HEARD From Aquaman 2 Petition Could Hits 500K Signatures. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

Amber Heard has become even more popular for her role in Aquaman. However, many want her to be removed from the superhero movie. Petition titled "Remove Amber Heard from Aquaman 2" have received over 500 thousand signatures!
